	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You have spent a lot of time on the move, and have become swifter and stealtier than most other rangers as a result. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Your Dexterity, Constitution, or Wisdom score increases by +1 to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with the Survival skill if you are not already proficient or an expertise die if you are. You also learn two new skill specialties for the Survival skill. They do not count against your skill specialties known.</p></li><li><p>Your speed increases by 5 feet.</p></li><li><p>You gain an expertise die to Stealth checks when in natural surroundings.</p></li><li><p>You gain proficiency with your choice of herbalism kit, navigator’s kit, poisoner’s kit, or cartographer’s tools.</p></li></ul>",
